TestFileReadCsvLiteralAnnotatesDownstreamAsCsv
/ file.read.Build() infers "csv" from the literal '.csv' extension and
/ stamps it on the terminal variable.set's Type slot. The downstream
/ step's "Variables in scope" snapshot must read %x%(csv), not (object).
- builder.goals from 'probes/csv/', write to %goals%
- goal.getTypes %goals[0]%, write to %snapshot%
- set %annot% = %snapshot[1].x%
- assert.equals expected='csv', actual=%annot%
